00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:06.240
The fallout from the raid, I think, is really&nbsp;
important. For a lot of women, it took a lot of&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:06.240 --> 00:00:11.264
courage. After the raid, there were so many women&nbsp;
who just weren’t going to go again.

