Who knows what trauma people have experienced
at the hands of&nbsp;cops, right? Like...

00:00:15.135 --> 00:00:16.419
Or just men? You know, you

00:00:16.419 --> 00:00:21.320
think you’re in this really awesome, safe space,&nbsp;
and to have that stripped away that quickly... It&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:21.320 --> 00:00:26.161
was brutal to watch people’s faces and bodies just&nbsp;
shrink in on themselves.

00:00:26.161 --> 00:00:29.087
We had to do a lot of&nbsp;work

00:00:29.087 --> 00:00:35.240
to try and make people feel comfortable about&nbsp;
coming back. And so, our numbers really dwindled,&nbsp;&nbsp;

