could be at conflict with the law — so, racialized&nbsp;
people, trans people, sex workers — it wasn’t as&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:48.040 --> 00:00:50.186
much of a safe space for them anymore

00:00:50.186 --> 00:00:52.211
because&nbsp;you never know when the 
