I think it felt like what we wanted, our&nbsp;
desires, our identities, our sexual liberation&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:00.880 --> 00:01:06.360
was not okay. Definitely affected me. I would&nbsp;
guess that it affected other people in the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:06.360 --> 00:01:12.200
sense of it’s just another form of bullying and&nbsp;
a profound one because you’re just being told,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:12.200 --> 00:01:16.431
“Oh, yeah? You think you can create this&nbsp;
beautiful, wonderful thing? Nah.”

00:01:16.431 --> 00:01:19.511
It was all so enraging.

