The differential impacts, the&nbsp;knowledge that 
that was happening across the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:23.080 --> 00:01:30.080
board for a whole bunch of people who committed&nbsp;
no crime, but for a night out had their lives&nbsp;&nbsp;

